00:38:47.410 --> 00:38:50.860 align:middle line:84%
I think our loved ones are
busy having their own life,

00:38:50.860 --> 00:38:53.560 align:middle line:84%
but they're only a thought,
a heartbeat, a breath away,

00:38:53.560 --> 00:38:56.380 align:middle line:84%
